{"tid":268153,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分手一年仲好掛住ex你問我答","createTime":"2017-06-02T20:09:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T07:47:45.000Z","uid":92727,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"146a1e6d49b8e243d71b3340c0d9937308bd81f8","tid":268153,"uid":92727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T20:09:44.000Z","msg":"夜晚又係亂諗野既時候，訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bcd9c6abd260b6e4b6891c871bc700c583e4e55","tid":268153,"uid":48577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T20:11:51.000Z","msg":"訓啦"},{"pid":"8f1a50ed59b888cf4fad8a584b471a462042c32b","tid":268153,"uid":92727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T20:12:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>訓啦</blockquote><br />\n佢就生日，前日諗諗下送唔送禮物比佢好就突然病發返，本身已經冇發作好幾個月。眼光光到七點先訓到"},{"pid":"740c0e977f6112565e1a288ae75716105ef5acc8","tid":268153,"uid":120581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T20:14:01.000Z","msg":"講句生日快樂咪算囉送咩姐"},{"pid":"3303dcf6892b86a09e2330c13e9c0914135e1354","tid":268153,"uid":92727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T20:15:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講句生日快樂咪算囉送咩姐</blockquote><br />\n點只禮物，直程想寫埋信之後生日個日掛個袋係佢屋企門口"},{"pid":"92a934ca4f3ce24fff28ebee8a8d0ab27365cadf","tid":268153,"uid":61264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T20:15:21.000Z","msg":"送乜野姐<br />\n佢剩係會覺得煩鳩住架咋"},{"pid":"3199a582e69556af467f9e6d3f5b3b36c2a32f24","tid":268153,"uid":120581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T20:17:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講句生日快樂咪算囉送咩姐</blockquote><br />\n點只禮物，直程想寫埋信之後生日個日掛個袋係佢屋企門口</blockquote><br />\n想吓好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9fcb8193416e3c381c182e52967d2065dea25c5","tid":268153,"uid":92727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T20:18:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>送乜野姐<br />\n佢剩係會覺得煩鳩住架咋</blockquote><br />\n一齊左四年，都係送份禮物姐，都煩😞😞😞"},{"pid":"46717c7c5f5e436add8df1981cb9a02f097ea4c4","tid":268153,"uid":99381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T20:19:16.000Z","msg":"一齊左幾耐？<br />\n其實唔係好明d人分手好耐都唔捨得/為分手要生要死<br />\n真係會咁中意一個人咩？"},{"pid":"eee965983adf634de0d41adc2207b6202acaff5c","tid":268153,"uid":92727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T20:21:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一齊左幾耐？<br />\n其實唔係好明d人分手好耐都唔捨得/為分手要生要死<br />\n真係會咁中意一個人咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n四年啊絲打。我自己都唔明，生活冇左佢都係要照過。我曾經以為自己放低左，但每次見到佢新伴侶都會個心chok一chok"},{"pid":"a9e59f5a5e8425eb585bea272b0b41c8201e7e48","tid":268153,"uid":64247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T20:21:21.000Z","msg":"屌，唔撚好呀，分咗手仲到佢好想搏乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00cecbecc965e4d365025aaf64998c399a66e2f7","tid":268153,"uid":92498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T20:21:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a983bb1bf5c65fc26acfb5d518f737294b6ef0a","tid":268153,"uid":92727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T20:22:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你試下諗佢同人地扑野既情境  更加訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打你好過份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb52dd1168bf57c3536525d74888720fa8eba4eb","tid":268153,"uid":92727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T20:24:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌，唔撚好呀，分咗手仲到佢好想搏乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能其實我依家做咩，I mean寫信送禮物，都只係自己打飛機自我感覺良好"},{"pid":"55854616c76dc6e952c109abd965dd11e396f22d","tid":268153,"uid":56508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T20:33:37.000Z","msg":"我以為自己開咗post"},{"pid":"e15f1bf7b230ad0d2a94382534a50c2b25aaff07","tid":268153,"uid":48577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T20:35:30.000Z","msg":"人地唔鐘意你 你做咩佢都覺得煩啦"},{"pid":"e2536907b8a4d30f72d2fa089416310f1edfbbf3","tid":268153,"uid":92727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T20:35:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我以為自己開咗post</blockquote><br />\n同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"4e148aeccd7e70b8b5e4d186bb26676f173703a4","tid":268153,"uid":92727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T20:36:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地唔鐘意你 你做咩佢都覺得煩啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e084efe32a471e8ba3ae12cf0bbb5b6368136cb1","tid":268153,"uid":92727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T20:39:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我以為自己開咗post</blockquote><br />\n你同你ex都好啊仲有溝通，我已經冇同佢講野好耐。只係上星期有日黑雨，好大聲行雷嘈醒左我。我同佢住好近，我知佢都聽到，佢以前好驚行雷，我就打比佢一傾就傾左兩個鐘。真係好開心，只係，我依家同佢只可以係過去式...."},{"pid":"8e36fcf8439efc70bdf9eebf1b588776a6622f34","tid":268153,"uid":61264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T20:44:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>送乜野姐<br />\n佢剩係會覺得煩鳩住架咋</blockquote><br />\n一齊左四年，都係送份禮物姐，都煩😞😞😞</blockquote><br />\n分左手就乜撚都係假"},{"pid":"62280d22a1576ddf2002620ca38937bac22d31e4","tid":268153,"uid":45756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T20:46:06.000Z","msg":"分左手半年 佢依家有新男朋友<br />\n但係呢半年我仲係晚晚掛住佢 成日訓唔著<br />\n你點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30ee733ee92f3f179dd5fb1075f3badc53b2f804","tid":268153,"uid":44085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T20:48:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講句生日快樂咪算囉送咩姐</blockquote><br />\n點只禮物，直程想寫埋信之後生日個日掛個袋係佢屋企門口</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢前兩日生日 我同你諗法一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後尾無做到，廢事佢當我痴漢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"639472af937a5a0feac398a30c11ea24002223d5","tid":268153,"uid":61264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T20:49:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分左手半年 佢依家有新男朋友<br />\n但係呢半年我仲係晚晚掛住佢 成日訓唔著<br />\n你點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n除左你個ex之外<br />\n你個世界係咪乜野都冇？"},{"pid":"b10d500e31b46ed659bee7a08ea5f91612500c02","tid":268153,"uid":92727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T20:57:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分左手半年 佢依家有新男朋友<br />\n但係呢半年我仲係晚晚掛住佢 成日訓唔著<br />\n你點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nI know that feel bro，分左手頭三四個月我都晚晚訓唔著。之後連chur左兩個o camp，之後開學，就少左好多諗佢"},{"pid":"63d82d617b5c555e499d010222e486c678b01282","tid":268153,"uid":92727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T20:58:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講句生日快樂咪算囉送咩姐</blockquote><br />\n點只禮物，直程想寫埋信之後生日個日掛個袋係佢屋企門口</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢前兩日生日 我同你諗法一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後尾無做到，廢事佢當我痴漢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇後悔？"}]}